data.name: ReadCashReceiptDetail
data.value: select distinct T1.CRV_IDENTIFIER, T1.CST_IDENTIFIER, T1.CRT_IDENTIFIER, T1.CRD_ID, T1.COLLECTION_AMOUNT from CKT_CR_DETAIL T1 join CKT_CRDTL_BAL_ADJ T2 on (T1.CRD_ID = T2.CRD_S_IDENTIFIER) and (T1.CRV_IDENTIFIER = T2.CRV_S_IDENTIFIER) and (T1.CST_IDENTIFIER = T2.CST_S_IDENTIFIER) and (T1.CRT_IDENTIFIER = T2.CRT_S_IDENTIFIER) and (@crdIdentifier = T2.CRD_IDENTIFIER) and (@crvIdentifier = T2.CRV_IDENTIFIER) and (@cstIdentifier = T2.CST_IDENTIFIER) and (@crtIdentifier = T2.CRT_IDENTIFIER)

data.name: ReadCashReceiptDetailCashReceiptCashReceiptDetailStatHistory1
data.value: select T1.CRV_IDENTIFIER, T1.CST_IDENTIFIER, T1.CRT_IDENTIFIER, T1.CRD_ID, T1.INTERFACE_TRAN_ID, T1.ADJUSTMENT_IND, T1.RECEIVED_AMOUNT, T1.COLLECTION_AMOUNT, T1.COLLECTION_DATE, T1.OBLGOR_PRSN_NBR, T1.REFUNDED_AMT, T1.DISTRIBUTED_AMT, T1.CLT_IDENTIFIER, T2.RECEIPT_AMOUNT, T2.CASH_RECEIPT_ID, T2.RECEIPT_DATE, T2.RECEIVED_DATE, T2.CREATED_BY, T3.CDS_IDENTIFIER, T3.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T3.REASON_CODE_ID, T3.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T3.REASON_TEXT, T4.CODE, T5.CR_SRCE_TYPE_ID, T5.CODE, T5.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T5.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T6.RECEIVED_DATE, T7.CODE from CKT_CR_TYPE T7 join CKT_CR_DETAIL_STAT T4 join CKT_CRSRC_TYPE T5 join CKT_CR_EVENT T6 join CKT_CASH_RECEIPT T2 join CKT_CR_DETAIL T1 on (T1.INTERFACE_TRAN_ID = @interfaceTranId) and (T1.ADJUSTMENT_IND <> 'Y') and (T1.CRD_ID >= @crdId) and (T2.CRT_IDENTIFIER = T1.CRT_IDENTIFIER) and (T2.CST_IDENTIFIER = T1.CST_IDENTIFIER) and (T2.CRV_IDENTIFIER = T1.CRV_IDENTIFIER) and ( (cast(@createdBy as char(8)) = ' ') or (T2.CREATED_BY = @createdBy) ) on (T6.CREVENT_ID = T2.CRV_IDENTIFIER) and (T6.CST_IDENTIFIER = T2.CST_IDENTIFIER) and ( (cast(@receivedDate1 as date) = cast(@date as date)) or (T6.RECEIVED_DATE >= @receivedDate1) ) and ( (cast(@receivedDate2 as date) = cast(@date as date)) or (T6.RECEIVED_DATE <= @receivedDate2) ) on (T5.CR_SRCE_TYPE_ID = T6.CST_IDENTIFIER) and (T5.CODE = @code1) join CKT_CRDTL_STATHIST T3 on (T1.CRD_ID = T3.CRD_IDENTIFIER) and (T1.CRV_IDENTIFIER = T3.CRV_IDENTIFIER) and (T1.CST_IDENTIFIER = T3.CST_IDENTIFIER) and (T1.CRT_IDENTIFIER = T3.CRT_IDENTIFIER) and (T3.DISCONTINUE_DATE > @discontinueDate) on (T4.CRDETAIL_STAT_ID = T3.CDS_IDENTIFIER) and ( (cast(@code2 as char(10)) = ' ') or (T4.CODE = @code2) ) on (T7.CRTYPE_ID = T2.CRT_IDENTIFIER) and (T7.CODE in ('FCRT REC', 'FDIR PMT')) order by T2.CASH_RECEIPT_ID desc, T1.CRD_ID

data.name: ReadCashReceiptDetailStatus
data.value: select top(1) CRDETAIL_STAT_ID, CODE from CKT_CR_DETAIL_STAT where (CRDETAIL_STAT_ID = @crdetailStatId) and ( (cast(@code as char(10)) = ' ') or (CODE = @code) )

data.name: ReadCashReceiptSourceType
data.value: select top(1) CR_SRCE_TYPE_ID, CODE, EFFECTIVE_DATE, DISCONTINUE_DATE from CKT_CRSRC_TYPE where CR_SRCE_TYPE_ID = @crSrceTypeId

data.name: ReadCashReceiptType1
data.value: select top(1) CRTYPE_ID from CKT_CR_TYPE where CRTYPE_ID = @crtypeId

data.name: ReadCashReceiptType2
data.value: select CRTYPE_ID, CODE from CKT_CR_TYPE where (CRTYPE_ID = @crtypeId) and (CODE in ('FCRT REC', 'FDIR PMT'))

data.name: ReadCollectionType
data.value: select top(1) COLLECTION_TYPE_ID, CODE from CKT_COLLTN_TYPE where COLLECTION_TYPE_ID = @collectionTypeId
